{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "翔竜山の山頂付近には",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Near the summit of Mount Shoryu"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔王城が作られようとしていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "a demon lord's castle was about to be built."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "まだまだ作り始めたばかりの城であり、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It was a castle just beginning to be constructed,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "玉座の間と呼ぶべき魔王の部屋にすら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and even in the demon lord's chamber that should be called the throne room,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "現在も多くの魔物が忙しそうに働いていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "many demons were busily working."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほーんと、突貫工事って感じ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Really feels like rushed construction."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　これが魔王の新しい城だなんてねぇ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I can't believe this is supposed to be the new castle of the demon lord.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔王ランスの部下である、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saizel, a subordinate of Demon Lord Rance,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔人サイゼルが魔王の部屋を見渡しながら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the demon Saizel, glanced over the demon lord’s room,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "呆れ気味に溜め息を吐きだした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and let out a sigh, somewhat exasperated."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「これから……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"From now on..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　一体、どうなってしまうのかしら」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "What on earth will happen?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それ、魔人である私達が考えても",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even if we demons think about it,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　意味ないんじゃない？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it probably doesn't mean anything, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは……そうなのよね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That's... true...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「結局、私達魔人は魔王様の命令に、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"After all, we demons cannot"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　逆らうことは出来ないのだから」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "disobey the orders of the demon lord.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そそ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Exactly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　人類を殺せっていうなら、そうするし、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If he says to kill humans, we do so,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　人類圏には不可侵だって言うなら従うだけ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and if he says humans’ territory is off-limits, we just obey.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"............\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……んもう。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Geez."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そんな顔しなくても心配いらないわよ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You don't have to make that face, there's no need to worry."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ランスの奴、人間の頃と性格変わってないし」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance hasn’t changed his personality since when he was human.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うん……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　確かに……そうかもね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That's probably true...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔王様ー！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Demon Lord!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔王様、どこにいらっしゃいますかー！？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Demon Lord, where are you!?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そう、変化なんて何もない。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, nothing has changed at all."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　サテラが魔王狂いになったこと以外はね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Except that Satera has become obsessed with the demon lord...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今、サテラのこと馬鹿にしたかー！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Did you just mock Satera!?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うっさいわねー。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You're so noisy."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それより何を騒いでるのよ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "More importantly, what’s all the fuss about?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔王様がどこにもいないんだ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The demon lord is nowhere to be found..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いったい、どこに行ってしまわれたのか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Where on earth has he gone...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……はあ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Sigh."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今度の主はほんっと、落ち着きがないわね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "This new master really has no composure...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「む、魔王様の悪口は、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I, Satera, will not forgive insults against the demon lord."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　このサテラが許さないぞ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あー、はいはい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ハウゼル、どこ行ったか知ってる？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hauser, do you know where he went?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さあ……私にも……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well... I don't know either..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今朝までは部屋にいらっしゃったと思ったけど」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I thought he was in the room until this morning.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あ、シルキィ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, Silky."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔王様がどこに行ったか知らないかしら？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Do you know where the demon lord went?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「え、魔王様いないの？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh, the demon lord isn’t here?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "毎日寝る間も惜しんで働く魔物達を不憫に思い、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Feeling sorry for the demons who work tirelessly every day without rest,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "手伝いとして巨大な鉄骨を運んでいた",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Silky, a small demon, was helping carry huge steel beams."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "小柄な魔人、シルキィが振り返る。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The petite demon Silky looked back."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私も知らないけど……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I don't know either, but..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あ、まさかあれかしら」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Ah, could it be that thing?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「む、なんだ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh, what is it?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さっき雑談してる時に話してたの」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We were just chatting earlier and talking about it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「どうやらワーグ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Apparently, Warg"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　また魔物の森で暮らしてるらしいから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "is living again in the demon forest,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんとか一緒に暮らせないかしら、って」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and they're thinking about whether they can somehow live together.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……それだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...That's it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それねえ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That, huh...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ワーグを迎えに行かれたのかしら。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Maybe the demon lord went to pick up Warg."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あれで魔王様、お優しいところがあるから」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "After all, the demon lord has a kind side.\""
    }
  ]
}

